parameters.name: EffectiveBandwidthFilter
parameters.description: The filter works based on the actual bandwidth. Enter a positive integer. Unit: Mbit/s.

parameters.name: MaxResults
parameters.description: The number of entries to return on each page. Valid values: **1** to **100**. Default value: **20**.

parameters.name: NextToken
parameters.description:
The pagination token that is used in the next request to retrieve a new page of results.

*   If **NextToken** is empty, no next page exists.
*   If a value of **NextToken** is returned, the value indicates the token that is used for the next query.

parameters.name: TrafficQosPolicyId
parameters.description: The ID of the QoS policy.

parameters.name: TrafficQosQueueDescription
parameters.description:
The description of the QoS queue.

This parameter is optional. If you enter a description, it must be 1 to 256 characters in length and cannot start with http:// or https://.

parameters.name: TrafficQosQueueName
parameters.description:
The name of the QoS queue.

The name must be 1 to 128 characters in length, and cannot start with http:// or https://.

parameters.name: TransitRouterAttachmentId
parameters.description: The ID of the inter-region connection.

parameters.name: TransitRouterId
parameters.description: The ID of the transit router.
